# Files NOT to copy into the Docker image.
# The Dockerfile itself controls what to COPY in.
# We only exclude:
#   - secrets (env, git)
#   - dev/test caches
#   - IDE metadata
# README.md and tests ARE copied because the Dockerfile wants them.
__pycache__
*.pyc
*.pyo
.git
.gitignore
.env
.env.*
.venv
venv
.pytest_cache
.coverage
htmlcov
*.log
.idea
.vscode
docs
